POSTCARDS FROM... @arpanarayamajhi⁣
⁣
“I have missed the summer in New York. This year the city is magnetic. Apparently the 90s and early 20s were a lot like this, and I feel it's my way of living the teenage dream that I had when I saw how cool New York was in the movies! Love,⁣

Arpana”.
